    "In this section, we present studies that proposed transformer-based prompt-specific trait scoring AES.",
    "Table 5 presents the summary of the studies with essay representation mechanisms and datasets employed.",
    "Hierarchical multi-task learning for trait scoring: Xue et al. (2021) developed a hierarchical multi-task learning approach that involves fine-tuning BERT for multi-dimensional AES tasks.",
